main event: Two unidentified flying objects were observed at James Connally AFB, Texas, on March 5, 1965.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for only 3 seconds, The objects were reported to be flying at a level flight, The observation was made visually from the ground, The report indicated insufficient data to explain the phenomenon, The objects were seen briefly before passing behind a tree and disappearing.
witness description: A2C Terry L Thomas, Dispatcher, Base Operations and a duty supervisor at the 440th Tactical Fighter Squadron.
